{"tid":776152,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都係好自卑","createTime":"2018-08-11T18:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T02:10:36.000Z","uid":200102,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d7a71b980770d8bd1e9b2d8e372e172a47306a57","tid":776152,"uid":200102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"唉我自己本身又唔靚 又身材唔好<br />\n讀書唔係特別叻 有好多興趣但冇樣精<br />\n好多嘢都堅持唔到<br />\n見到啲強勢少少啊 有自信嘅就淆曬底<br />\n講嘢又唔醒目 對住陌生人就好怕尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成日覺得人地見到我個樣同身形已經唔想識我<br />\n<br />\n仲要前排去完u reg day<br />\n見到啲又靚又social 嘅人 真係好葡萄佢地可以咁世界<br />\n真係好憎自己啲毒撚格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc771fc18a76b20d9fd6f9e5a842f3c2483c7cb4","tid":776152,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:32:49.000Z","msg":"有,比女飛完仲自卑"},{"pid":"9a9388ba517eb05d11b79c8c7c0d14c9667d0c99","tid":776152,"uid":200102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc771fc18a76b20d9fd6f9e5a842f3c2483c7cb4","tid":776152,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:32:49.000Z","msg":"有,比女飛完仲自卑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:43:04.000Z","msg":"因咩事先"},{"pid":"ebfed5b55552d45753bcdd69c3c4216ad0cc1700","tid":776152,"uid":200183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:47:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2cd9951560a1d2b5ac184e73158b21fbe884e49","tid":776152,"uid":196700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T19:47:25.000Z","msg":"自卑一陣好啦<br />\n<br />\n成長必經階段 <br />\n<br />\n識朋友啦 一定有真心夾得埋既人既"},{"pid":"24cc07cde767bd97b48d7c57336c57689b7692ac","tid":776152,"uid":154980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T21:00:36.000Z","msg":"樓豬加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒自卑不如努力改變自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然我都好自卑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e44b8302e36a16e719dafe9503ef679a553a563","tid":776152,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T21:07:01.000Z","msg":"你仲有四年進步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be451649fff53c823c499bf02adfaf645a14012","tid":776152,"uid":193476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T21:38:00.000Z","msg":"其實好多時人會自卑，都可能係身邊既人做成，例如屋企人成日鬧呀，睇唔起，都好影響自信。<br />\n<br />\n我好相信真正既你，並無你講得咁差。<br />\n<br />\n試下逐樣逐步改善啦。<br />\n身形唔好，做多啲運動。<br />\n樣未夠靚，剪個髮，有自信唔化妝都可以好有氣質。<br />\n<br />\n一個人天然，有信心，自然會有一種吸引人既氣質。樣貌唔係最重要。"},{"pid":"b0c6cab2e9531cd934ee1f2198c5ae3953f22d5b","tid":776152,"uid":139211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T21:59:38.000Z","msg":"一個人點都會有自卑感，冇人生而完美嘛<br />\n<br />\n最緊要唔好成日放大自己缺點，<br />\n你一定有自己既優點只係你自己將自己既唔好放太大<br />\n而見唔到自己既好姐<br />\n<br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35a11e2b5bca4313ba58270aeda37577c7a1e19","tid":776152,"uid":200102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T00:29:47.000Z","msg":"好多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55403d91754be2c423cbccfca8d69ff665e76edb","tid":776152,"uid":132478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T01:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb69f35058aeaf577a04286e